solution.explanation:
The missing block is:
route {
  cidr_block = "10.50.0.0/16"
  gateway_id = aws_vpn_gateway.vpn.id
}
Putting every route inline inside one aws_route_table resource means there's a single source of truth — no more standalone aws_route resource for Terraform to reconcile away.
